snippet.title: Beyond Melee Demo 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD: https://beyondmelee.com/download/

Beyond Melee is an in-depth mod for Super Smash Bros. Melee which sets out to build an entirely new experience on top of the game as a base. New characters, stages, mechanics, and completely reworked designs of existing characters and stages make Beyond Melee a brand new experience worth trying.

For more information, check out the Beyond Melee Presentation: https://youtu.be/54ElOnXn_II

Songs used: Battle Tower Remix by NyxTheShield, Termina Field Metal Cover by RichaadEB

Discord: https://beyondmelee.com/discord/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Beyond_Melee

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/BeyondMelee
